&lt;p&gt;The Sales Manager will drive the performance and growth of the sales organization in pursuit of being the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(1) Contractor of Choice&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; for homeowners and the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(2) Employer of Choice&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; for employees.&lt;/p&gt;
